      "name": "Construct stiffness QoI comparison — FEA vs. experimental (N=11)",
      "description": "Mean predicted stiffness within 6.2% of experimental mean across both laboratories; E/uval = 1.41, within the pre-established acceptance bound of 1.96. Validation metric satisfied."
    },
    {
